msgid "Identity"
msgstr "识别"

#. Translators: search terms to find this application. Do NOT translate or localize the semicolons! The list MUST also end with a semicolon!
#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.desktop.in.in:10
msgid "Movie;Film;Clip;Difference;Frame;Quality;"
msgstr "电影;影片;剪辑;不同;帧;画质;"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:10
msgid "A program for comparing multiple versions of an image or video."
msgstr "一个用来对比一张图片或一个视频的多个版本的程序。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:58
msgid "This release contains translation updates."
msgstr "此版本包含翻译更新。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:60
msgid "Added Dutch translation (thanks Heimen Stoffels)."
msgstr "增加荷兰语翻译（感谢 Heimen Stoffels）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:61
msgid "Added French translation (thanks Lapineige)."
msgstr "增加法语翻译（感谢 Lapineige）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:62
msgid "Added Spanish translation (thanks Óscar Fernández Díaz)."
msgstr "增加西班牙语翻译（感谢 Óscar Fernández Díaz）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:68
msgid "This release fixes minor UI issues."
msgstr "此版本修复几个界面上的小问题。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:70
msgid "When closing a file, the next “tab” is now selected, or, if closing the last file, the previous one is selected."
msgstr "现在，当关闭一个文件时，下一个“标签页”会被选中。如果关闭的是最后一个文件，那么前一个“标签页”会被选中。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:71
msgid "Fixed the application title not showing up upon closing all files."
msgstr "修复了关闭所有文件时应用程序标题不显示的问题。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:77
msgid "First release."
msgstr "第一版。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:94
msgid "Ivan Molodetskikh"
msgstr "Ivan Molodetskikh"

#. Translators: file chooser file filter name.
#: src/window.rs:869
msgid "Videos and images"
msgstr "视频和图像"

#. Translators: file chooser dialog title.
#: src/window.rs:880
msgid "Open videos or images to compare"
msgstr "打开视频或图像以比较"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:40
msgid "This release contains translation updates and minor UI changes."
msgstr "此版本包含翻译更新和几处界面小更改。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:42
msgid "Video rotation tag is now respected."
msgstr "现在更推荐使用视频旋转标签。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:43
msgid "Added Deutsch translation (thanks Johannes Hayeß)."
msgstr "增加德国翻译（感谢 Johannes Hayeß）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:44
msgid "Added Finnish translation (thanks Jiri Grönroos)."
msgstr "增加芬兰语翻译（感谢 Jiri Grönroos）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:45
msgid "Added Croatian translation (thanks Milo Ivir)."
msgstr "增加克罗地亚语翻译（感谢 Milo Ivir）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:46
msgid "Added Italian translation (thanks Blackcat-917)."
msgstr "增加意大利语翻译（感谢 Blackcat-917）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:47
msgid "Added Brazilian Portuguese translation (thanks Gustavo Costa)."
msgstr "增加巴西葡萄牙语（感谢 Gustavo Costa）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:48
msgid "Added Slovak translation (thanks Jose Riha)."
msgstr "增加斯洛伐克语翻译（感谢 Jose Riha）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:49
msgid "Added Swedish translation (thanks Åke Engelbrektson)."
msgstr "增加瑞典语翻译（感谢 Åke Engelbrektson）。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:50
msgid "Added translation contribution link."
msgstr "增加贡献翻译链接。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:51
msgid "Specified input device recommendations to improve display in the new GNOME Software."
msgstr "指定的输入设备建议，以改善新的 GNOME Softwear 中的显示。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:52
msgid "Label on the main window can now wrap so as not to restrict minimum window size."
msgstr "为了不限制最小窗口尺寸，主窗口的标签现在能够伸缩啦。"

#: data/org.gnome.gitlab.YaLTeR.Identity.metainfo.xml.in.in:24
